### Chat with Brendan (start a Test Video Gen run)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/chat/brendan
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

{
  "user_id": "demo",
  "message": "Make a Test Video Gen run about LangGraph"
}

### Check run status
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/runs/{{runId}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### Get HITL approval links (ideate, prepublish)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/hitl/link/{{runId}}/ideate
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

GET http://localhost:8080/v1/hitl/link/{{runId}}/prepublish
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### Approve HITL gates directly (when you already have the token)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/hitl/approve/{{runId}}/ideate?token={{token}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

GET http://localhost:8080/v1/hitl/approve/{{runId}}/prepublish?token={{token}}
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### List artifacts for a run (via API helper route, if exposed)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/runs/{{runId}}/artifacts
x-api-key: {{API_KEY}}

### Webhook endpoints (used by providers; shown here for reference)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/webhooks/kieai
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: {{requestId}}
X-Timestamp: {{epochSeconds}}
X-Signature: {{hmacSignature}}

{ ...provider-payload-here... }

POST http://localhost:8080/v1/webhooks/upload-post
